        Our Certifications

        Team of Experts

        Dr. Peter Josling – The Garlic Guru

        Known as the “Garlic King”, Dr. Peter Josling is the creator of the world's first stabilized and patented Allicin extract, which is formulated into capsules, liquids, gels, and creams. His groundbreaking work in garlic-based health solutions has revolutionized the way we approach natural healing. Through his expertise, Dr. Josling has brought a powerful, scientifically-proven antioxidant to the forefront of alternative medicine.

        Dr. Rajiv Gaur - Senior Ayurveda Acharya

        Associate Professor Panchkarma with 10 years of expertise in Ayurveda, Dr. Rajiv Gaur specializes in Diabetes and Pain Management. He is a skilled practitioner for treating joint pain, cervical pain, low back pain, acidity, constipation, and liver-related ailments. Dr. Rajiv’s holistic approach focuses on restoring balance to the body through personalized Ayurveda therapies, ensuring effective, long-lasting relief.

        Dr. Garima Gaur - BAMS D Pharma

        With over 8 years of experience in Ayurveda, Dr. Garima Gaur focuses on Women’s Health, Diabetes, and Pain Management. She specializes in conditions such as PCOD, Leucorrhea, and Cancer care, helping her patients achieve better well-being through a blend of traditional wisdom and modern practices. Her expertise offers comprehensive solutions for chronic health issues, empowering women to lead healthier lives.

        Dr. Devender Kaushik - MD Panchkarma

        Dr. Devender Kaushik is a specialist in Panchkarma with 10 years of experience in Ayurvedic treatments. As an Associate Professor of Panchkarma, Dr. Kaushik integrates ancient healing practices with modern techniques to promote detoxification and rejuvenation. His methods are renowned for their precision, ensuring that each patient receives a treatment plan tailored to their unique needs, enhancing their overall health and vitality.
